OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775469931
OL,3,CLife-size replica of Turin Shroud on
OL,4,Cdisplay at Blackburn Cathedral
OL,6,FIan White, Chief Operating Officer of
OL,7,FBlackburn Cathedral, says the Turin
OL,8,FShroud embodies the Easter story
OL,10,FA life-size replica of the burial
OL,11,Fshroud believed to have been used to
OL,12,Fwrap the body of Jesus after his
OL,13,Fcrucifixion is on show at Blackburn
OL,14,FCathedral.
OL,16,FThe replica of the Turin Shroud, one
OL,17,Fof only five in the World, is being
OL,18,Fdisplayed as part of the cathedral's
OL,19,Fcentenary celebrations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
