PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775469931
OL,3,CLife-size replica of Turin Shroud on
OL,4,Cdisplay at Blackburn Cathedral
OL,6,FThe Shroud of Turin is a length of
OL,7,Flinen cloth that bears a faint image
OL,8,Fof the front and back of a crucified
OL,9,Fman.
OL,11,FIt is believed by many to be the
OL,12,Factual burial Shroud used to wrap the
OL,13,Fbody of the Lord Jesus after his
OL,14,Fcrucifixion, and upon which his bodily
OL,15,Fimage is miraculously imprinted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
