OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775469931
OL,3,CLife-size replica of Turin Shroud on
OL,4,Cdisplay at Blackburn Cathedral
OL,6,FIn addition to the life-size replica
OL,7,Fof the Shroud, an accompanying
OL,8,Fexhibition features evidence revealed
OL,9,Fby historical and scientific research,
OL,10,Fexplaining how the Shroud's image and
OL,11,Fbloodstains align with Gospel accounts
OL,12,Fof Jesus' death and resurrection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
