OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1775469931
OL,3,CLife-size replica of Turin Shroud on
OL,4,Cdisplay at Blackburn Cathedral
OL,6,FIan White, Chief Operating Officer of
OL,7,FBlackburn Cathedral, acknowledges that
OL,8,Fsome historians have questioned
OL,9,Fwhether the actual Turin Shroud is a
OL,10,Fforgery: "The exhibition does a really
OL,11,Fgood job of explaining how that doubt
OL,12,Fhas come into the story....but the
OL,13,Fscientific investigations continue and
OL,14,Fsome of the newer studies have placed
OL,15,Fthe cloth to be of that exact age,
OL,16,Fover 2 thousand years old."
OL,18,FThe Turin Shroud exhibition at
OL,19,FBlackburn Cathedral is free to enter
OL,20,Fand is open every day until 12th April
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
